      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in peerless condition. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of true showroom caliber, exhibiting no discernible wear and possessing a documented history of fastidious care. Every surface and mechanical component reflects an uncompromising standard of excellence. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than the definitive example of this model, this offering stands as a benchmark of automotive preservation.",
